  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute, until fragrant.",
    "Stir in the Egyptian ful medames, briny feta cheese, cooked noodles, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Cook for 2-3 minutes, until the cheese is melted and the noodles are well coated.",
    "Stir in the chopped fresh parsley and lemon juice.",
    "Season with additional salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the noodle stir-fry in a scallop shell, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
